lyrics:
[verse]
In Calatayud, where Enzo resides
A young warrior with dreams so wide
Seven years old, yet wise beyond his years
A future legend, it's crystal clear

[chorus]
Enzo, oh Enzo, you're growing so strong
A warrior's heart, where courage belongs
On this special day, we celebrate your might
Blasting through life, like Iron Maiden's might
